data.description: OPEN HOUSE SAT DEC. 9 & SUN DEC. 10 1-3. Awesome location! This property is modern and bright and offers 3 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms in the heart of desirable Stone Oak!  Elegant open floor plan boasts 1825 sqft. of functional living space with fantastic designer finishes throughout. The focal point of this home lies in its well-appointed kitchen, featuring stainless steel appliances, recently updated countertops, a breakfast bar, freshly painted cabinets, and an oversized sized pantry. The kitchen effortlessly flows into the dining space and family room ideal for gathering and entertaining.  Upstairs, discover 3 large bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms plus a bonus loft where you can read, relax or utilize as an at-home work space. The backyard is quiet and includes a wooden deck with plenty of room to BBQ. There are no neighbors behind. Outstanding NEISD schools. Johnson High School! Convenient to hospitals, the San Antonio Airport and trendy restaurants and shops.
